BG(1)

NAME
    bg - run a command as a reattachable background job

SYNOPSIS
    bg path [arg ...]

DESCRIPTION
    bg is a shell built-in alias for runelf_bg. It starts an ELF program as a
    reattachable background job.

    The path is resolved the same way as other shell commands, so command
    names may omit directory prefixes and the .elf suffix.

SEE ALSO
    runelf_bg(1), jobs(1), fg(1), kill(1)
